issues.description: The constructor in the solution repository uses the parameter order (String lectureName, int numberOfInscribedStudents, int numberOfGuestStudents, int numberOfLecturers, int numberOfTutors), which does not match the order specified in the UML diagram and the problem description (numberOfInscribedStudents, lectureName, numberOfLecturers, numberOfGuestStudents, numberOfTutors). Students following the UML will implement the constructor differently and encounter compilation or test failures.
